dct_title_s: Kingdom of Hungary principality of Transylvania, Sclavonia, Croatia, with a part of Valakia, Bulgaria, Bosnia and Servia from the latest surveys ascertained by astronomical observations.
dct_description_sm: Shows upper and lower Hungary, Croatia, Sclavonia and Transylvania. Relief shown by hachures. Prime meridian: Ferro. 1 map: hand col.; 45 x 53 cm This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
